(23, 23, 156, 51, '<p style="text-align: center">\r\n	<span style="font-size: 18px"><span style="color: #ff0000"><strong>关于包邮：东北 陕西限申通汇通快递！<strong><font color="#ff0000" size="4">贵州、内蒙古、广西、云南</font></strong>半价包邮，限申通。海南、青海、西藏、新疆、宁夏、甘肃只需付首重！其他地区圆通、汇通、申通！不明之处，可咨询客服！感谢您对我们的支持！</strong></span></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;<span style="color: #ff00ff"><span style="font-size: 24px">宝贝描述：</span></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color: #ff00ff"><span style="font-size: 24px">宝贝名称：生态棉尿布</span></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color: #ff00ff"><span style="font-size: 24px">宝贝颜色： 本白</span></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color: #ff00ff"><span style="font-size: 24px">尺寸规格：45*17cm（误差2cm内）</span></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color: #ff00ff"><span style="font-size: 24px">宝贝特点：100%纯棉<strong><span style="color: #ff0000"><span style="font-size: 36px">两大层6小层</span></span></strong>哦~透气 舒适柔软 让宝宝穿的更舒心 成长更健康 我们妈妈也可以更加的放心！！！</span></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color: #ff00ff"><span style="font-size: 24px"><img onload=''if(this.width>600)makesmallpic(this,600,800);'' align="absMiddle" onload="if(this.width&gt;600)makesmallpic(this,600,800);" src="http://img03.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i3/743185507/T22RqCXgdaXXXXXXXX_!!743185507.jpg" /></span></span></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	<span style="color: #ff00ff"><span style="font-size: 24px"><img onload=''if(this.width>600)makesmallpic(this,600,800);'' align="absMiddle" onload="if(this.width&gt;600)makesmallpic(this,600,800);" src="http://img04.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i4/743185507/T2j.ewXe0XXXXXXXXX_!!743185507.jpg" /><img onload=''if(this.width>600)makesmallpic(this,600,800);'' align="absMiddle" onload="if(this.width&gt;600)makesmallpic(this,600,800);" src="http://img04.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i4/743185507/T20oawXfxXXXXXXXXX_!!743185507.jpg" /><img onload=''if(this.width>600)makesmallpic(this,600,800);'' align="absMiddle" onload="if(this.width&gt;600)makesmallpic(this,600,800);" src="http://img04.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i4/743185507/T2rEewXeNXXXXXXXXX